'''Explore''' is an [[emote]] unlocked after completing 600 [[Clue scroll (beginner)|beginner clue scrolls]]. Performing this emote consists of leaning forward, searching in exploration, and then taking out a [[sextant]] to navigate instead.

As of 17 March 2022, there are '''1,728''' current members that have unlocked the Explore emote.

